 Photo taken on Nov. 26, 2021 shows a giant Christmas tree and the sound and light show at the Grand Place during the Winter Wonders in Brussels, Belgium. Featuring activities like the sound and light show, Christmas market and so on, the Winter Wonders 2021 in Brussels started on Friday. With rising numbers of COVID-19 cases, strict measures were imposed during the event, such as checking COVID Safe Tickets, wearing face masks and keeping distance. (Xinhua/Zhang Cheng)   Photo taken on Nov. 26, 2021 shows a giant Christmas tree and the sound and light show at the Grand Place during the Winter Wonders in Brussels, Belgium. Featuring activities like the sound and light show, Christmas market and so on, the Winter Wonders 2021 in Brussels started on Friday. With rising numbers of COVID-19 cases, strict measures were imposed during the event, such as checking COVID Safe Tickets, wearing face masks and keeping distance. (Xinhua/Zhang Cheng)  People visit the Christmas Market during the Winter Wonders in Brussels, Belgium, Nov. 26, 2021. Featuring activities like the sound and light show, Christmas market and so on, the Winter Wonders 2021 in Brussels started on Friday. With rising numbers of COVID-19 cases, strict measures were imposed during the event, such as checking COVID Safe Tickets, wearing face masks and keeping distance. (Xinhua/Zhang Cheng)  People walk past a signboard of COVID-19 prevention and control measures at the Christmas Market during the Winter Wonders in Brussels, Belgium, Nov. 26, 2021 Featuring activities like the sound and light show, Christmas market and so on, the Winter Wonders 2021 in Brussels started on Friday. With rising numbers of COVID-19 cases, strict measures were imposed during the event, such as checking COVID Safe Tickets, wearing face masks and keeping distance. (Xinhua/Zhang Cheng)  People visit the Christmas Market during the Winter Wonders in Brussels, Belgium, Nov. 26, 2021. Featuring activities like the sound and light show, C